@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="about-page">

    <div class="container">

        <!-- Card 1 -->

        <div class="about-card left" data-aos="fade-right">

            <h1>About Happy Hearts</h1>

            <p>
                Welcome to <strong>Happy Hearts</strong>, where every pet has a story, and every customer who walks through our doors is beginning a new journey.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->

        <div class="about-card right" data-aos="fade-left">

            <h2>Our Story</h2>

            <p>
                At Happy Hearts, we believe that pets are more than just animals—they become family. They bring companionship, comfort, joy, and unforgettable memories into our lives. Whether you're welcoming your very first pet or adding a new member to your growing family, we're here to help you every step of the way.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->

        <div class="about-card left" data-aos="fade-right">

            <h2>Our Pets</h2>

            <p>
                Our store proudly offers a wide variety of healthy and well-cared-for pets, including beautiful freshwater and saltwater fish, playful rabbits, affectionate cats, loyal dogs, and other small companions. Every pet we provide is selected with care because we believe every animal deserves a loving home.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- Card 4 -->

        <div class="about-card right" data-aos="fade-left">

            <h2>Pet Supplies & Accessories</h2>

            <p>
                But Happy Hearts is more than just a pet store. We are passionate about helping pet owners create the best possible environment for their companions. That's why we stock a carefully selected range of high-quality pet supplies and accessories, including:
            </p>

            <ul class="about-list">

                <li> Aquariums and fish tanks</li>

                <li> Water pumps and filtration systems</li>

                <li> Fish nets and aquarium maintenance equipment</li>

                <li> Decorative ornaments and aquatic plants</li>

                <li> Pet toys and enrichment products</li>

                <li> Food and nutritional supplies</li>

                <li> Essential care products and accessories</li>

            </ul>

        </div>

        <!-- Card 5 -->

        <div class="about-card left" data-aos="fade-right">

            <h2>Supporting Every Pet Owner</h2>

            <p>
                Whether you're setting up your very first aquarium, upgrading your existing habitat, or searching for the perfect toy to keep your pet entertained, our knowledgeable team is always ready to offer advice and guidance.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- Card 6 -->

        <div class="about-card right" data-aos="fade-left">

            <h2>Our Commitment</h2>

            <p>
                We understand that every pet owner has different needs, which is why we strive to provide products that are reliable, affordable, and designed to help your pets live happy, healthy lives.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- Card 7 -->

        <div class="about-card left" data-aos="fade-right">

            <h2>Our Belief</h2>

            <p>
                At Happy Hearts, we believe that the bond between people and animals has the power to reduce stress, inspire happiness, and create lasting connections. Whether you're drawn to the calming beauty of a tropical fish, the playful energy of a rabbit, the loyalty of a dog, or the comforting companionship of a cat, you'll find more than a pet here—you'll find a lifelong friend.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- Card 8 -->

        <div class="about-card right" data-aos="fade-left">

            <h2>Thank You</h2>

            <p>
                Thank you for making Happy Hearts part of your journey. We look forward to helping you discover the perfect companion and everything you need to give them a happy, healthy home.
            </p>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>